\fs20\lang1033\langfe2052\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp2052 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8987722 \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 
Foxit is a leading software provider of fast, affordable, and secure PDF solutions. Businesses and consumers increase productivity by using Foxit\hich\f1 \rquote \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 
s cost effective solutions to securely work with PDF documents and forms. Software developers reduce costs and improve time to market with Foxit\hich\f1 \rquote \loch\f1 
s Software Development Kits (SDKs) to incorporate robust PDF technology into their application workflows. This\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1  \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 technology shares the same underlying technology that powers Google\hich\f1 
\rquote \loch\f1 s open-source PDFium project. Winner of numerous awards, Foxit boasts over 275 million users and has sold to over 100,000 customers located in over 200 countries. Since Foxit products are\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1  
\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 ISO 32000-1/PDF 1.7 standard compliant, they are compatible with other PDF products like those from Adobe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs12 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs12\up6\insrsid8987722 \loch\af1\dbch\af31505\hich\f1 \'ae}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1 
